    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About <i>LIGHT THE BEACON</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>LIGHT THE BEACON</i> is a 2D <strong>action-adventure survival game</strong> with <strong>rogue-like</strong> elements, set in the depths of a <strong>sci-fi apocalyptic</strong> universe. Take on the role of a genetically engineered <strong>Ranger</strong>, humanity’s last hope, as you navigate the dangers of space, maintain your ship, and battle for survival against hostile <strong>AI creations</strong>.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/d8e57c771b4453c6930366e8a0f33ee7.poster.avif?t=1745614814\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/d8e57c771b4453c6930366e8a0f33ee7.webm?t=1745614814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/d8e57c771b4453c6930366e8a0f33ee7.mp4?t=1745614814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive in Hostile Space</strong>: Pilot your customizable ship through derelict stations and forgotten sectors, scavenging for critical resources to keep your crew alive while defending against relentless AI forces and unknown threats.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/edadd049f9560f86314dc4434c7df838.poster.avif?t=1745614814\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/edadd049f9560f86314dc4434c7df838.webm?t=1745614814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/edadd049f9560f86314dc4434c7df838.mp4?t=1745614814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Universe</strong>: Explore an ever-changing galaxy where no two playthroughs are the same. Each sector is filled with new challenges, enemies, and opportunities for discovery.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/e85a7b333fbbdfeef968a9e9ad480e0c.poster.avif?t=1745614814\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/e85a7b333fbbdfeef968a9e9ad480e0c.webm?t=1745614814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/e85a7b333fbbdfeef968a9e9ad480e0c.mp4?t=1745614814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Permadeath and Tension</strong>: Every decision counts. Face <strong>permadeath</strong> and start again from scratch if you fail to light the beacons and secure your survival. Tension builds as your supplies dwindle and your ship's integrity is pushed to its limits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable Ships</strong>: Craft and upgrade your ship with modular parts to suit your playstyle. Equip weapons, improve defenses, and balance resource manage<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/cb655dafb2dad069151ce7d6703d3574.poster.avif?t=1745614814\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/cb655dafb2dad069151ce7d6703d3574.webm?t=1745614814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268900/extras/cb655dafb2dad069151ce7d6703d3574.mp4?t=1745614814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>ment to adapt to the dangers of the universe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AI-Driven Threats</strong>: In the aftermath of the <strong>Great AI Cataclysm</strong>, hostile AI entities control the void. Battle against corrupted machines and alien AI as you uncover the remnants of a lost civilization.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration and Discovery</strong>: Venture into forgotten sectors, uncover hidden lore, and piece together the mystery of humanity’s collapse. Your journey will be filled with unexpected encounters and choices that shape your experience.</p></li></ul>",
